    <p>The content of this line can be set in preferences (see 
    <xref href="../preferences/gui_options.dita#gui_options" type="topic">GUI options</xref>). Available variables are the same as for the export module (see 
    <xref href="../lighttable/export_selected_usage_filename.dita#export_selected_usage_filename" type="topic">filename template</xref>). You can also add new lines by using 
    <codeph>$(NL)</codeph>variable.</p>
    <p>Position of the infos line can also be set in preferences (see 
    <xref href="../preferences/gui_options.dita#gui_options" type="topic">GUI options</xref>).</p>
